{"tid":1573194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有半個月多d某國國慶,點解無人提早諗點慶祝?","createTime":"2019-09-16T02:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T14:29:49.000Z","uid":52939,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd4481e97a33abcc4e7789bdeecb0f13df90ae10","tid":1573194,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"大家都知港豬出名善忘同free ride,懶散<br />\n一次大型d既慶祝活動起碼都要一頭半個月先call得齊人同埋多人知<br />\n港豬和理非等仲要約齊親朋友好一齊參與同打咭號召,講緊最少都要大半個月<br />\n<br />\n適逢某國就黎國慶,大家都知啦,鍵國左幾十年,係威係晒,蟈民已經除撚晒褲打撚晒飛機<br />\n港豬點可以唔出一分力賀下佢? 咁樣對得住天地良心咩?? 人地咁&quot;愛&quot;你當你遊艇仔咁湊左咁多年?<br />\n<br />\n今日起鍵盤戰士要分d人手出黎全力討論點樣celebrate 個日!!!"},{"pid":"aaa1db1c92f2b86bddd10bf5333f4c3132d6d1f0","tid":1573194,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"34630b43e586d2af6aaa1e33a2fb374d35f8593d","tid":1573194,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"高鐵有冇計"},{"pid":"2a3fe30068bb77e3f9a542318fbb9bd682fb9849","tid":1573194,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"諗好曬"},{"pid":"fd24f8c54fd513511b46a0308dea1919720428e4","tid":1573194,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a3fe30068bb77e3f9a542318fbb9bd682fb9849","tid":1573194,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"諗好曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"講黎聽下"},{"pid":"0c0608dd57e9022392ef3030134263180f2e5975","tid":1573194,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:08:27.000Z","msg":"燒黨旗"},{"pid":"8b4597d650df8f9145aeae84d63724bce3432866","tid":1573194,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34630b43e586d2af6aaa1e33a2fb374d35f8593d","tid":1573194,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"高鐵有冇計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi